        <detaileddescription>
<para>Exports the batch of log records to their export destination. This method must not be called concurrently for the same exporter instance. The exporter may attempt to retry sending the batch, but should drop and return kFailure after a certain timeout. <parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
